She saw that the battle was over but didn't move from her hiding place in 
the bushes near the battle field.  She watched with some facination as to 
what was going on.  She over heard what the other bots were talking about 
without them ever knowing she was there.
Then her nose twitched.  She tried to hold it in but her nose got the better 
of her.  She let out an audio sneeze.
